| P6: registry-integration | 2 | `projects/<Name>.json` exists with status + absorbed_into + disposition |
| P7: deletion-gate-tooling-coverage | 1 | References `bin/repo-delete-gate.sh/.ps1` OR explicitly explains why the gate is not required |

