## How to Reproduce

1. List all `*.md` files in `audits/absorption-justifications/`.
2. For each file, score against the 7 pillars in `registry/audit-absorption-justification/schema.json`.
3. Sum earned points; map to grade via `grade_boundaries`.
4. Sort by `score` ascending (weakest first → most informative for improvement).
5. Aggregate into `GRADES.json` + `GRADES.md`.

